          About this item

          • Voice Control: These color changing recessed lights could easily be controlled by voice via the APP once you connected these recessed lights with your Wi-Fi. Compatible with Alexa/Google Assistant. PS: Only compatible with Wi-Fi of 2.4GHz, can't work with dimmer
          • Easy Management: After set them with Wi-Fi, you could add these recessed lighting to group. There are timing setting and series of automated operations to help you to control them, make your life more comfortable. PS: There is only one chance to add them to the area(like kitchen, bedroom, etc.) when setting, otherwise you have to reset and set them again. There will be few seconds delay of controlling when you turn off the on/off switch and turn it on again, power failure would do the same
          • Super Performance: There are 16 million colors, music mode and 8 scenes, meets all your demands! PS: Music mode is only available for single light, not for group. You can't go back to scene selection at music mode, but you could go back to the desktop of your phone and use other APP
          • Series White: With the adjustable range from 2700K to 6000K, you can choose white color from ultra warm white to pure white and adjust the brightness from 5-100%
          • Compact Dimensions: Cut-Out size is 2-5/8'', front diameter is 3-1/4'', fits 2.5-3'' hole

          Product Description

          Time Manage

          Use the timer to set the on/off time, no need to consider about forgetting to turn off the lights ever!

          There are also a series of automated operations to help you to control the lights, make your life more comfortable!

          Remote Control

          These RGB smart lighting could be added to group after set them with Wi-Fi.

          Once they are connected with the App, you could remote controlling the lights when you are about to back.

          Choose your favourite color to light up your house!

          Series White

          With the adjustable range from 2700K to 6000K, you can choose white color from ultra warm white to pure white and adjust the brightness from 5~100%.

          There are also 16 million colors, music mode and 8 scenes, meets all your demands!

          How customer reviews and ratings work

          Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

          To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
